WEBVTT

1
00:00:04.862 --> 00:00:08.170
tequila and tonicwith a wedge of lemon.

2
00:00:12.927 --> 00:00:16.558
no ring 'cause you're single
or because you don't likewearing one ?

3
00:00:16.604 --> 00:00:18.380
You asking me if I'm married ?

4
00:00:18.805 --> 00:00:20.191
Are you married ?

5
00:00:20.396 --> 00:00:21.936
No. not anymore.

6
00:00:23.174 --> 00:00:24.325
Ana-lucia.

7
00:00:25.041 --> 00:00:26.839
So tell me. ana-lucia.

8
00:00:26.898 --> 00:00:31.336
why are you drinking tequilaan tonics at ten to noon ?

9
00:00:31.641 --> 00:00:33.191
I hate flying.

10
00:00:33.978 --> 00:00:36.655
and they stuck me all the wayin the back of the plane.

11
00:00:36.690 --> 00:00:38.152
So where are you sitting ?

12
00:00:38.370 --> 00:00:39.723
23-B.

13
00:00:39.743 --> 00:00:40.867
Wanna trade ?

14
00:00:41.803 --> 00:00:45.746
I can't do this. ma !
He's not supposedto be mine !

15
00:00:46.039 --> 00:00:47.754
It was neverpart of the plan.

16
00:00:55.849 --> 00:00:59.876
Excuse me. would you mindwatching my bag for a moment ?
I'll be right back.

17
00:01:00.625 --> 00:01:02.410
- Sure. whatever.
- Thank you.

18
00:01:02.868 --> 00:01:04.277
what's goin' on ?

19
00:01:04.441 --> 00:01:07.283
My flight to L. A. Leavesin a couple of hours. so...

20
00:01:07.318 --> 00:01:09.737
you want to do one more bumpfor the road ?

21
00:01:10.077 --> 00:01:11.014
Uh...

22
00:01:15.805 --> 00:01:16.732
<i>Fate</i>

23
00:01:17.266 --> 00:01:18.534
<i>or coincidence ?</i>

24
00:01:22.788 --> 00:01:26.874
my husband keeps reminding me
that planes want to bein the air.

25
00:01:26.968 --> 00:01:28.741
Well. he sounds likea very smart man.

26
00:01:28.776 --> 00:01:31.511
You be sure and tell him that
when he gets backfrom the bathroom.

27
00:01:45.619 --> 00:01:47.838
a plane breaks apart

28
00:01:48.108 --> 00:01:50.808
somewhere over the south pacific.

29
00:02:22.516 --> 00:02:23.467
she's not breathing.

30
00:02:23.490 --> 00:02:24.195
Watch out.

31
00:02:32.867 --> 00:02:34.781
good. Let it out.

32
00:02:35.474 --> 00:02:36.695
You okay ?

33
00:02:37.811 --> 00:02:39.466
Where's my mom ?

34
00:02:43.623 --> 00:02:46.617
<i>Two groups of passengers survive...</i>

35
00:02:49.177 --> 00:02:53.490
<i>separated on different sides of the same island.</i>

36
00:03:04.444 --> 00:03:05.553
Come on !

37
00:03:06.727 --> 00:03:07.772
Come on !

38
00:03:10.191 --> 00:03:12.339
big. deep breaths ! Big breaths !

39
00:03:20.474 --> 00:03:22.904
move ! Move ! Get her up !

40
00:03:44.229 --> 00:03:45.251
Excuse me.

41
00:03:46.366 --> 00:03:48.371
Would youlook after the children ?

42
00:03:49.346 --> 00:03:51.084
There is somethingI have to do.

43
00:03:51.835 --> 00:03:53.092
Uh. okay.

44
00:03:54.722 --> 00:03:57.822
Stay with this nice woman. I'll be back in a minute.

45
00:04:01.497 --> 00:04:02.706
<i>Recovery...</i>

46
00:04:02.941 --> 00:04:05.889
help ! Hey ! I need some help !

47
00:04:06.171 --> 00:04:08.672
Someone in the jungleis alive !

48
00:04:09.529 --> 00:04:11.301
please help me !

49
00:04:11.854 --> 00:04:13.192
<i>And rescue.</i>

50
00:04:13.732 --> 00:04:14.802
help !

51
00:04:16.233 --> 00:04:17.607
What's your name ?

52
00:04:17.659 --> 00:04:18.528
Bernard !

53
00:04:18.587 --> 00:04:20.642
You're gonna be all right. bernard.

54
00:04:21.346 --> 00:04:23.237
we need to finda safer place.

55
00:04:23.260 --> 00:04:26.372
Well. what aboutthe signal fire ?
How are we all gonna get rescued

56
00:04:26.595 --> 00:04:28.121
if we're off the beach ?

57
00:04:28.156 --> 00:04:31.079
They have satellites. the black box.

58
00:04:31.314 --> 00:04:33.510
We don't need a firefor them to find us.

59
00:04:33.545 --> 00:04:36.642
Yes. we do.
Before the crash.

60
00:04:36.865 --> 00:04:40.593
we were flying for two hoursin the wrong direction.

61
00:04:40.993 --> 00:04:42.672
They don't know where to look.

62
00:04:49.423 --> 00:04:53.237
You were the one
who pulled the dead bodiesout of the water ?

63
00:04:53.413 --> 00:04:54.434
Yes.

64
00:04:54.775 --> 00:04:56.959
Were any of themafrican-american ?

65
00:04:56.982 --> 00:04:57.865
No.

66
00:04:58.382 --> 00:04:59.697
It's my wife.

67
00:05:00.155 --> 00:05:01.764
I can't find her.

68
00:05:02.926 --> 00:05:04.488
I will pray for her.

69
00:05:05.016 --> 00:05:07.623
<i>Desperation...
and hope...</i>

70
00:05:07.763 --> 00:05:10.605
your husband was inthe tail section of the plane ?

71
00:05:10.851 --> 00:05:14.187
Yes. he was. but he'll be back.

72
00:05:16.100 --> 00:05:18.050
You think he's still alive ?

73
00:05:18.578 --> 00:05:20.349
I know he is.

74
00:05:20.384 --> 00:05:21.264
How ?

75
00:05:22.662 --> 00:05:24.153
I just do.

76
00:05:25.762 --> 00:05:29.061
we must have beenat about 40.000 feet
when it happened.

77
00:05:30.178 --> 00:05:31.868
Hit an air pocket.

78
00:05:31.904 --> 00:05:34.369
dropped and blacked out.

79
00:05:34.499 --> 00:05:35.990
I saw the whole thing.

80
00:05:36.048 --> 00:05:38.326
I knew that the tail was gone. but I...

81
00:05:39.462 --> 00:05:41.752
couldn't bring myselfto look back...

82
00:05:43.008 --> 00:05:44.346
and then

83
00:05:44.628 --> 00:05:46.789
the front endof the plane broke off.

84
00:05:48.654 --> 00:05:50.685
Well. it's not hereon the beach.

85
00:05:51.448 --> 00:05:52.799
neither is the tail.

86
00:05:55.394 --> 00:05:57.965
what are you doingin here ? What's in the bag ?

87
00:05:57.989 --> 00:06:01.140
Booze. smokes. couple"playboys."

88
00:06:01.340 --> 00:06:02.361
What's in yours ?

89
00:06:02.397 --> 00:06:03.430
Medicine.

90
00:06:03.864 --> 00:06:05.860
Just about sums it up. don't it ?

91
00:06:05.919 --> 00:06:08.749
You do this back home. too. steal from the dead ?

92
00:06:08.784 --> 00:06:12.175
Just not lookin'at the big picture. doc.
You're still backin civilization.

93
00:06:12.245 --> 00:06:13.267
And where are you ?

94
00:06:13.290 --> 00:06:14.418
I'm in the wild.

95
00:06:16.836 --> 00:06:18.692
Do you play checkerswith your pop ?

96
00:06:19.428 --> 00:06:20.227
No.

97
00:06:20.990 --> 00:06:23.068
I live in australiawith my mom.

98
00:06:23.233 --> 00:06:26.250
She got sick. She dieda couple of weeks ago.

99
00:06:26.602 --> 00:06:28.188
You're having a bad month.

100
00:06:28.223 --> 00:06:29.436
I guess.

101
00:06:29.859 --> 00:06:32.195
- I just want to know.
- Well. you're not gonna know.

102
00:06:32.231 --> 00:06:34.966
-  What's the big deal ?
- It's not a big deal.

103
00:06:34.995 --> 00:06:36.533
It's just that you

104
00:06:37.167 --> 00:06:38.964
and your tattoos...

105
00:06:39.726 --> 00:06:40.795
don't add up.

106
00:06:44.059 --> 00:06:46.677
so what is it about that guy
that makes you all

107
00:06:47.135 --> 00:06:48.661
weakin the loins ?

108
00:06:49.521 --> 00:06:52.034
Do  you try to be a pigor it just come naturally ?

109
00:06:52.961 --> 00:06:54.699
So he's a doctor. right ?

110
00:06:54.758 --> 00:06:56.824
Hell. give me a couple ofband-aids.

111
00:06:56.859 --> 00:06:59.231
a bottle of peroxide.
I could run this island. too.

112
00:07:00.185 --> 00:07:02.698
You're actually comparingyourself to jack ?

113
00:07:03.015 --> 00:07:05.574
The difference between usain't that big. sweetheart.

114
00:07:07.230 --> 00:07:08.944
are you all right ?

115
00:07:09.819 --> 00:07:11.157
No. I'm okay.

116
00:07:11.897 --> 00:07:13.400
It just can't happen.

117
00:07:13.611 --> 00:07:14.468
What ?

118
00:07:14.985 --> 00:07:16.676
Can't grow upin this place.

119
00:07:17.603 --> 00:07:19.341
what are welooking for again ?

120
00:07:19.564 --> 00:07:24.523
Any long piece of metalor plastic tubing.
anything that looks likeit would work as a frame.

121
00:07:25.604 --> 00:07:26.919
Am I being punished ?

122
00:07:26.966 --> 00:07:29.197
What. you think workin'with your old man is punishment ?

123
00:07:29.244 --> 00:07:30.443
Feels like punishment.

124
00:07:30.479 --> 00:07:33.484
This is us taking controlof our destiny.

125
00:07:33.661 --> 00:07:35.833
<i>While some prepare to leave...</i>

126
00:07:37.216 --> 00:07:38.778
I think we shouldgo back. man.

127
00:07:40.058 --> 00:07:41.373
Suit yourself.

128
00:07:41.713 --> 00:07:44.951
<i>Others uncover reasons to stay.</i>

129
00:07:44.987 --> 00:07:45.867
Boone.

130
00:07:47.264 --> 00:07:49.014
you need thismore than I do.

131
00:07:55.614 --> 00:07:56.883
what is that ?

132
00:08:00.370 --> 00:08:02.260
that's what we're gonnafind out.

133
00:08:05.895 --> 00:08:08.020
<i>The crash was only the beginning.</i>

134
00:08:08.455 --> 00:08:10.533
<i>This group must now fight</i>

135
00:08:10.568 --> 00:08:14.759
<i>to survive attacks
by mysterious island inhabitants.</i>

136
00:08:18.752 --> 00:08:21.053
the kids ! They took the kids !

137
00:08:26.924 --> 00:08:28.274
They're gone.

138
00:08:31.128 --> 00:08:32.338
What is that ?

139
00:08:32.385 --> 00:08:33.594
It's a list.

140
00:08:33.665 --> 00:08:35.262
A list of what ?

141
00:08:35.367 --> 00:08:36.647
Of us.

142
00:08:38.602 --> 00:08:39.659
nothing ?

143
00:08:39.809 --> 00:08:43.661
They dragged nine peopleinto the jungle. the kids.

144
00:08:43.690 --> 00:08:45.292
and there's no signof 'em ?

145
00:08:46.120 --> 00:08:48.353
Now's not a good timeto talk ?

146
00:08:49.263 --> 00:08:51.737
What needs to happento make you say something ?!

147
00:08:51.754 --> 00:08:53.759
Hey. calm down. Let's figure this out.

148
00:08:53.783 --> 00:08:57.012
Here are the names of everysingle person they took.

149
00:08:57.047 --> 00:08:59.830
what they were wearing. what they look like.

150
00:08:59.877 --> 00:09:02.520
One of themhad a list of us.

151
00:09:02.708 --> 00:09:03.999
Maybe they're watching us.

152
00:09:04.516 --> 00:09:06.606
You were gonefor two hours yesterday.

153
00:09:06.852 --> 00:09:07.897
- What ?
- Where were you ?

154
00:09:07.933 --> 00:09:10.175
- I was going to the bathroom.
- Hey. stop.

155
00:09:11.467 --> 00:09:14.189
Let's not get paranoid here.
We don't know anything.

156
00:09:14.236 --> 00:09:18.534
Why would they try toinfiltrate us ? That's crazy.

157
00:09:18.557 --> 00:09:23.156
well. whoever they are. they know we are here.
We need to leave this beach.

158
00:09:31.446 --> 00:09:32.526
Five minutes.

159
00:09:32.549 --> 00:09:34.508
We've been walkingfor three days straight. ana.

160
00:09:34.531 --> 00:09:35.964
And you're still here.

161
00:09:36.163 --> 00:09:37.643
You want to keep walking.

162
00:09:37.878 --> 00:09:38.911
go ahead.

163
00:09:39.381 --> 00:09:40.731
Fresh water.

164
00:09:40.825 --> 00:09:44.656
rock wall at ourbacks. lots of fruit trees.
Right herelooks pretty good to me.

165
00:09:47.509 --> 00:09:48.355
Hey.

166
00:09:49.341 --> 00:09:50.175
Hey.

167
00:09:50.889 --> 00:09:53.483
Do you really think it'spossible that one of us is...

168
00:09:55.468 --> 00:09:56.513
one of them ?

169
00:09:56.936 --> 00:09:59.046
Why do you thinkI'm digging this hole ?

170
00:09:59.715 --> 00:10:02.204
<i>Suspicion turns to paranoia...</i>

171
00:10:02.697 --> 00:10:03.825
oh. hey. ana.

172
00:10:08.480 --> 00:10:11.263
<i>but has the real threat been discovered ?</i>

173
00:10:12.225 --> 00:10:13.364
What are you doing ?

174
00:10:13.905 --> 00:10:17.157
Let me out of hereright now.
You let me out. You let me out !

175
00:10:19.994 --> 00:10:21.168
He wasn't on the plane.

176
00:10:21.192 --> 00:10:21.820
What ?

177
00:10:21.855 --> 00:10:25.366
We were in the airfor two hours.
I didn't see him once. not once.

178
00:10:25.389 --> 00:10:27.115
It's a big plane. ana. Just because you didn't...

179
00:10:27.139 --> 00:10:29.417
- no. I didn't see him. either.
- Oh. you're not all serious.

180
00:10:29.440 --> 00:10:31.575
He never talks about himself. nathan.

181
00:10:31.598 --> 00:10:34.827
Every time I ask him anything. he just dodges.

182
00:10:35.132 --> 00:10:36.835
We should let him go.

183
00:10:37.434 --> 00:10:39.287
We're not savages.

184
00:10:39.533 --> 00:10:42.481
If I were a savage. I would'vecut off his finger already.

185
00:10:43.561 --> 00:10:44.794
That's tomorrow.

186
00:10:45.475 --> 00:10:46.729
I'll pull you up.

187
00:10:47.422 --> 00:10:48.666
Grab the rope.

188
00:10:51.003 --> 00:10:52.529
Ana-lucia'S...

189
00:10:52.588 --> 00:10:55.183
I think we all thinkthat she's gonna hurt you.

190
00:10:55.897 --> 00:10:59.114
Now you need to get awayfrom here.
There's some fruit in there. Now just go.

191
00:11:04.421 --> 00:11:05.254
what ?

192
00:11:05.277 --> 00:11:07.649
He's gone. Nathan's gone.

193
00:11:11.171 --> 00:11:12.803
All right. what are you gonna do ?

194
00:11:13.015 --> 00:11:15.220
They found us. It's time to move.

195
00:11:19.835 --> 00:11:22.711
<i>Amid violence and deception...</i>

196
00:11:24.414 --> 00:11:27.338
<i>how does a man find redemption ?</i>

197
00:11:27.432 --> 00:11:28.583
Why  aren't you talking ?

198
00:11:40.678 --> 00:11:41.793
what is it ?

199
00:11:42.894 --> 00:11:44.315
I don't know.

200
00:11:48.061 --> 00:11:50.456
looks like some sortof storage facility.

201
00:11:50.949 --> 00:11:51.816
hey.

202
00:11:52.297 --> 00:11:53.589
come over here.

203
00:12:11.147 --> 00:12:12.309
It's  a radio.

204
00:12:14.807 --> 00:12:16.721
Hello. Can anybody hear me ?

205
00:12:20.267 --> 00:12:21.758
the hills are blocking it.

206
00:12:21.794 --> 00:12:24.289
If we want a signal. we need to get to higher ground.

207
00:12:27.213 --> 00:12:29.338
Why do you thinkthey're doing this ?

208
00:12:29.690 --> 00:12:31.886
Why do I thinkwho's doing what ?

209
00:12:32.555 --> 00:12:33.505
Them.

210
00:12:34.198 --> 00:12:37.227
Don't you ever wonderwhy they attack us ?

211
00:12:37.990 --> 00:12:41.067
Maybe they're notattacking us.

212
00:12:43.185 --> 00:12:47.482
Yeah. they just drag us intothe jungle every now and then.

213
00:12:47.835 --> 00:12:49.561
No real harm done.

214
00:12:50.723 --> 00:12:52.574
Can I ask you something ?

215
00:12:53.455 --> 00:12:54.559
Sure. ana.

216
00:12:55.099 --> 00:12:56.719
The day of the crash...

217
00:12:58.950 --> 00:13:00.923
you ran out of the jungle

218
00:13:01.261 --> 00:13:04.408
ten minutes after the crash.
You weren't wet.

219
00:13:04.983 --> 00:13:07.097
you were nevereven in the ocean.

220
00:13:08.659 --> 00:13:09.551
Nathan.

221
00:13:09.938 --> 00:13:11.343
did you kill him ?

222
00:13:11.578 --> 00:13:13.609
Nathan was nota good person.

223
00:13:13.961 --> 00:13:16.556
That's whyhe wasn't on the list.

224
00:13:17.061 --> 00:13:18.717
What about the kids ?

225
00:13:18.869 --> 00:13:20.513
Did you kill them. too ?

226
00:13:20.572 --> 00:13:22.322
The children are fine.

227
00:13:23.355 --> 00:13:25.011
They're better off now.

228
00:13:55.171 --> 00:13:56.416
where's goodwin ?

229
00:14:01.304 --> 00:14:03.124
We're safe here now.

230
00:14:10.967 --> 00:14:12.400
<i>Silence...</i>

231
00:14:12.956 --> 00:14:14.541
<i>and suffering.</i>

232
00:14:19.449 --> 00:14:22.044
<i>how long must they last ?</i>

233
00:14:24.667 --> 00:14:26.134
It's going to be okay.

234
00:14:33.191 --> 00:14:34.981
What. you're talking now ?

235
00:14:37.118 --> 00:14:39.185
It's been 40 days.

236
00:14:40.641 --> 00:14:43.177
You've been waiting40 days to talk ?

237
00:14:45.920 --> 00:14:48.421
You waited 40 days to cry.

238
00:15:03.605 --> 00:15:06.444
john. people are talking
about what we're doingout here every day.

239
00:15:06.468 --> 00:15:08.792
especially since we nevercome back with anything.

240
00:15:09.227 --> 00:15:11.481
What we're doing hereis far more important.

241
00:15:13.466 --> 00:15:14.477
Right now.

242
00:15:15.158 --> 00:15:16.602
this is our priority.

243
00:15:17.659 --> 00:15:20.982
<i>Purpose. faith. determination.</i>

244
00:15:22.330 --> 00:15:24.079
<i>Where does it all lead ?</i>

245
00:15:24.713 --> 00:15:26.909
I had a dream last night.

246
00:15:27.062 --> 00:15:29.692
I asked for a sign. and

247
00:15:30.126 --> 00:15:33.750
then I saw a plane crash.
a beechcraft. right out there.

248
00:15:33.785 --> 00:15:35.241
It was a dream. but

249
00:15:35.570 --> 00:15:38.364
it wasthe most real thing
I've ever experienced.

250
00:15:39.844 --> 00:15:41.392
I know where to go now.

251
00:15:41.990 --> 00:15:43.165
Go for what ?

252
00:15:43.270 --> 00:15:45.572
To find what we needto open this bastard up.

253
00:15:50.827 --> 00:15:51.731
hello ?

254
00:15:51.989 --> 00:15:53.598
Hello ? Can anybody hear me ?

255
00:15:56.756 --> 00:15:58.130
Where do you thinkit came from ?

256
00:16:02.359 --> 00:16:03.509
He was a priest.

257
00:16:03.533 --> 00:16:06.281
Gold teeth. obviously well-off.

258
00:16:07.924 --> 00:16:09.192
What kind of money is that ?

259
00:16:09.239 --> 00:16:10.710
Nigerian naira.

260
00:16:10.746 --> 00:16:14.151
What is a nigerian priest
doing on an islandin the south pacific ?

261
00:16:14.491 --> 00:16:16.640
I'm not so surehe's a priest.

262
00:16:18.765 --> 00:16:20.362
Is that the plane you saw ?

263
00:16:20.831 --> 00:16:22.499
As  best I can tell.

264
00:16:23.720 --> 00:16:26.556
what's importantis what's inside it.

265
00:16:31.122 --> 00:16:31.968
boone !

